        <div class="layer"><h3>04. Adaptive AI Core</h3><p>Applies time-series learning, anomaly detection, classification, continuous self-learning, and baseline modeling.</p></div>
        <div class="layer"><h3>05. Intervention Layer</h3><p>Generates smart alerts, wellness recommendations, doctor-shareable reports, and emergency escalation if needed.</p></div>
      </div>
